{"tid":1853830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封關！？冠忠跨境巴士內部流出，求FC","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:36:46.000Z","uid":295688,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e55a2aa0f654047dc9e4cbdb955e28aab19111c7","tid":1853830,"uid":295688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:36:37.000Z","msg":"冠忠通知：<br />\n各位，這裡有重大事件宣佈。<br />\n特區政府正考慮未來兩天內會全面封關，包括我們運作開的深圳灣口岸。<br />\n有見及此，公司管理層與我們溝通過，封關日起，環島中港通店鋪全部暫停營業直到關口恢復正常運作。<br />\n所有前線同事們到時先清大假(如有)，否則接下來會停薪留職，由於無法估計直到何時開關。<br />\n暫時初步估算約2個月左右。究竟何時開始實施，要開政府宣佈。<br />\n另外，直到關口恢復正常後，不排除到時採取1更制，或半日制，公司仍在考慮中。<br />\n屆時有可能合約會重新再定立有關實際工時。<br />\n<br />\n冠忠再通知：<br />\n各位同事~因政府有意封閉所有關口,如一落實。所有前線同事需要放無薪假,直致另行通告。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"5abbe158f606a6228af5a4d89b95a2b61a48d9df","tid":1853830,"uid":295688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"有無人Fact Check ?"},{"pid":"4e729ca4c30efc463adbaf3205c9838d81719dba","tid":1853830,"uid":167559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"堅 or not ?"},{"pid":"4dd70494224c396d83dfb4ed25b8abf429772bb5","tid":1853830,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"求fc"},{"pid":"5766cb92c5f8b502d98e4ba37589b5b289741529","tid":1853830,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">16:30 咪開估囉 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a3b0b29fc7ba831db259928f49815a7a1b3814e","tid":1853830,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"堅定流 希望唔好炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dea40e2ee9593b7b61695bbb26553f2a86bdc66","tid":1853830,"uid":273218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"我只知<br />\n如果連登仔反對封關<br />\n佢早就封"},